*>    Set (TESTVAR1) to red if in error and * if blankACSHLIM
    IF (FLG-ACCT-STATUS-NOT-OK
    OR  FLG-ACCT-STATUS-BLANK)
    AND CDEMO-PGM-REENTER
        MOVE DFHRED             TO
             ACSTTUSC OF CACTUPAO
        IF  FLG-ACCT-STATUS-BLANK
            MOVE '*'            TO
             ACSTTUSO OF CACTUPAO
        END-IF
    END-IF
