*>
*>    Open Day
*>    COPY CSSETATY REPLACING
*>      ==(TESTVAR1)== BY ==OPEN-DAY==
*>      ==(SCRNVAR2)== BY ==OPNDAY==
*>      ==(MAPNAME3)== BY ==CACTUPA== .
*>vvv-> file: C:\Users\Sethulekshmi.Pishara\Work\LiberTools\CLERITY\Converter\aws_cards_demo\sources\cpy\CSSETATY.cpy
*>*****************************************************************
*> Copyright Amazon.com, Inc. or its affiliates.
